    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the demo for My Party Needs An Alchemist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this light-hearted fantasy adventure game, you play as an alchemist!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a quest to save the world with a party of brave adventurers that you would come to know and love! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE THE LEAFWOOD FOREST!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the first region of the game as you travel from quest to quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MAKE POTIONS! USE POTIONS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/fc9ec8d6fc7189529cdaa2ae95ada7d6.poster.avif?t=1740588493\" width=600 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/fc9ec8d6fc7189529cdaa2ae95ada7d6.webm?t=1740588493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/fc9ec8d6fc7189529cdaa2ae95ada7d6.mp4?t=1740588493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather herbs, mix them together and create wondrous Potions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use them when the time is right to fight off dangerous, magical beasts! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BECOME THE ULTIMATE SUPPORT!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/c799168c6832361ad48f9a4af1b1dbaa.poster.avif?t=1740588493\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/c799168c6832361ad48f9a4af1b1dbaa.webm?t=1740588493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/c799168c6832361ad48f9a4af1b1dbaa.mp4?t=1740588493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organise your party, meet new characters and help them to survive this legendary quest! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FALL IN LOVE WITH THE FIRST 4 COMPANIONS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/a5d2e9cbbacc238ba53f669dbe118f50.poster.avif?t=1740588493\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/a5d2e9cbbacc238ba53f669dbe118f50.webm?t=1740588493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258130/extras/a5d2e9cbbacc238ba53f669dbe118f50.mp4?t=1740588493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help save the world in this light-hearted character-driven story!</p>",
